    color: "$dark"
    lineHeightPx: 48.53
    text: 误区三：睡前喝酒助眠
- elementId: card3-body
  elementType: text
  bounds: [1320, 468, 480, 170]
  content:
    align: [justify, top]
    fontSize: 26.7
    fontFamily: Liter, MiSans
    color: "$dark"
    lineHeightPx: 42.12
    letterSpacing: 1.08
    text: 酒精虽能加速入睡，但会严重破坏睡眠结构——减少深度睡眠和REM睡眠，导致后半夜频繁醒来。长期依赖反而加重失眠，建议用温牛奶或泡脚替代。
